    이벤트 개요

    ◆ 이벤트 기간 ◆
    2020년 6월 25일 (목) 점검 후 ~ 7월 11일(토) 23:59

    ◆ 이벤트 개요 ◆
    이벤트 〈복각: 데드 히트 서머 레이스! ~꿈과 희망의 이슈타르컵 2019~ 라이트판〉 개최!
    이번 이벤트에서는 서번트들이 팀을 짜고
    이슈타르가 개최하는 레이스에 참가하여 순위를 경쟁합니다.
    레이스에 참가하는 여섯 팀 중 마음에 드는 팀을 선택하고 서포트하며
    결승선까지 이끌어 주세요!
    이 이벤트는 2부로 구성되어 있습니다.
    제1부 메인 퀘스트를 진행하면 '★4(SR) 이슈타르(라이더)'가
    이벤트 기간 동안 임시로 가입    합니다.

    제2부는 7월 2일(목)부터 개방될 예정입니다.
    제2부에 참가하기 위해서는 제1부 메인 퀘스트를 클리어해야 합니다.
    제2부에서는 새로운 맵, 새로운 이벤트 아이템이 등장!
    제2부의 메인 퀘스트를 클리어하면 '★4(SR) 이슈타르(라이더)'가 정식으로 가입합니다.

    제1부, 제2부를 모두 클리어하여 '★4(SR) 이슈타르(라이더)'를 획득하세요!
    ※ 이 이벤트는 2019년에 개최된 이벤트 〈데드 히트 서머 레이스! ~꿈과 희망의 이슈타르컵 2019~ 라이트판〉를 더욱 즐기기 쉽게 일부를 재조정한 '복각 라이트판 이벤트'입니다

    Race Support Procedure

    During this event, proceeding through the Main Quest will unlock the ｢Race Support Battles｣ where six teams will compete
    for the rankings. Clearing the Support Battle Quests of your selected team will earn you some ｢Support Points｣ and will move
    them closer to the finish line. Clear the quest of your favorite team and help them reach the finish line before the others!

    The racing progress of each team will depend on how much total Support Points have accumulated from all the Masters
    participating. Work together with other Masters who support the same team as you, and finish the race!

    Once the teams reach the finish line, Race Support Battles will end, and you'll receive a reward based on the winning team.
    Once the ｢Race Support Battles｣ are over, the current race will end, and the next race will begin.

    Press your favorite team's icon to view their Support Quests!
    Clear your favorite team's Support Battle Quests to help them win the race!

    ◆ Confirm the progress of the race by checking the remaining distance ◆
    Progress for each team during the race will be displayed as ｢remaining distance to the goal｣ under their team icon.
    When the race is getting tight, you can choose which team to support by checking their remaining distance.

    You can confirm each team's Support Battle progress
    by looking at the remaining distance under their icon!
    ◆ All participants will receive rewards based on the winning team ◆
    When all teams reaches the finish line, the rankings will be displayed and the race will proceed to the next round.
    Then all participants will receive rewards from the winning team.

    Each winning team's reward can be confirmed by pressing the Event Rewards button at the upper-right corner of the Terminal.
    ※ The ｢Winning Team's Reward｣ can be obtained by clearing the Main Quest of that round during the event period, even if the
    　　｢Race Support Battles｣ are already over.
    ※ The ｢Winning Team's Reward｣ will be sent to your Present Box.

    ◆ Gather Support Points to receive QP ◆
    Support Points can be gathered by clearing each teams's Support Battle Quest while the race is still in progress (before all
    teams reaches the finish line). You will receive QP according to the total Support Points you've gathered once the round is over.
    The QP you receive is unaffected by which team you supported or which team won the race.

    You'll receive more Support Points by clearing quests with a higher difficulty and by using Boost Items before the battle.
    Support Points can be confirmed by pressing the Event Rewards button at the upper-right corner of the Terminal screen.
    ※ During Race Support Battles, each team will take on different routes on the map and their position may not match their
    current rankings displayed at the top of the screen. Please note that the top 3 teams displayed will be always be the closest
    teams to the finish line.

    ◆ Progressing through the Main Quests ◆
    New areas on the map will appear once the top team reaches a certain point.
    Clearing the quests from those new areas will allow your Main Quests to proceed.
    ※ Even if the round is over, you will not be allowed to go to the next round without proceeding with the Main Quests first.
    　　Also, you can no longer return to a previous round once you've already moved on to the next one.
    ※ Depending on the time your participation, Support Battle Quests may have ended. Even though Main Quests are unaffected,
    　　you can no longer participate in Support Battle Quests once their period is over.
    ※ Once all Main Quest from Part 1 has been cleared, all rounds on the whole map will be restored and can participate in
    　　Support Battle Quests again.

    Hints and Strategies

    ◆ Hints and Strategies: Part 1 ◆
    Using Boost Items such as the ｢퀵 오일｣, ｢아츠 니트로｣, and ｢버스터 가솔린｣ which can be acquired from the Event Item
    Exchange shop or as quest rewards will grant you an advantage during battle when doing Support Battle Quests.
    You can select 1 of the Boost Items before starting a quest.
    ※ Boost Items affect all allies (including Sub Members) and will last the whole battle.


    퀵 오일 아츠 니트로 버스터 가솔린

    ■ Use Boost Items to increase Support Points you get!
    Clearing Support Battles with Boost Items will allow you to gain more (double) Support Points.

    Support Points +1 Support Points +2

    ■ Learn the compatibility to increase Support Points you get even further!
    Each Boost Item is compatible with certain teams. Using them on a compatible team will allow you to gain even more (triple)
    Support Points.

    Support Points +1 Support Points +3

    After selecting the Support Battle Quest for a team you wish to support, starting the quest will show a list of Boost Item Selection screen.
    The displayed number will be the bonus multiplier for that team, and the item which grants the highest value is the most compatible with your team.

    Once all Event Quests have been cleared, a 「Challenge Quest」 with an insane amount of difficulty will be unlocked.

    The Challenge Quest will not disappear once cleared, which means you can keep challenging the quest as many time as you
    prefer and try out different combination of Servants and Craft Essences.
    ※ Quest clear rewards and dropped items can only be obtained during your first clear.

    ◆ Challenge Quest Requirements ◆
    Only players who have completed ｢Final Singularity: Grand Time Temple - Solomon｣ can participate in this quest.
